p3a2

Class TrainNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • p3a2.TrainNode

  • public class TrainNode
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which allows for the creation of a basic "TrainNode" object which represents a single train in the inbound train management program(ITM). The Object will then presumably be used within another "Queue" class. Methods allow for : the creation of a TrainNode object and the various getters and setters associated with its properties ie get trainNum, set trainNum etc.
    Since:
    04/12/2014
